snippet.title: Wishing Sarah - Trailer
snippet.description:
Made in GBStudio, Wishing Sarah is a short GameBoy game that dwelves on the after events of Dreaming Sarah. It comes with a GB rom that you can use on emulators or the real thing!

Wishing Sarah is out now, part of the Spooky Station.

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/700100/Spooky_Station/

Itch.io: 
https://bakudas.itch.io/spooky-station

Trailer by the talented Fernanda Shimada:
https://www.youtube.com/user/joltjolteonreload
https://twitter.com/jojoruteon
